feed.title: Rob Keleher
feed.subtitle: I'm a senior full-stack software engineer, web developer, project owner, and team leader with a focus on intelligent design. I've worked on projects of all sizes, from SPAs to full-scale enterprise software servicing more than 16,000 users. I am also an avid fan of the Japanese language, culture, and foreign exchange with 2 years of experience working in Japan as an English teacher.
